blablamower 0.0.1 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.blablamower
Root package for the World Mower Application :)
com.blablamower.command
Apply to world the operations described in CommandEnum
com.blablamower.config
Spring configuration classes.
com.blablamower.controller
Controllers can handle requests to be performed.
com.blablamower.domain
Domain contains classes used to model the world.
com.blablamower.exception
Exceptions contain RuntimeExceptions that may happen if a business problem happened.
com.blablamower.factory
Factories allow to build domain objects from various description of these domain objects.
